high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the right of the dish washer.
Pick up the yellow knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the end of the counter on the right.
Cut the apple next to the stove into three parts.
Turn right and go to the front of the sink on the left.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go back to the end of the counter on the right.
Pick up one piece of apple from the counter.
Turn right and go back to the sink on the left.
Wash the apple piece in the sink under running water.
Turn around and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the apple piece on the shelf in the refrigerator.
